data.description: Inviting 4-year young home with an open floor plan and luxury vinyl flooring throughout, offering  both elegance and durability. The kitchen has gorgeous white cabinets with beautiful granite  countertops. 3 spacious bedrooms providing ample space for rest and relaxation.2 beautifully  appointed bathrooms, including a large master bathroom featuring a huge, tiled shower, perfect for  unwinding after a long day. Sprawling 1.7-acre lot with ample space for outdoor activities,  gardening, and entertainment. Centrally located in Gloucester, this home offers the perfect blend  of tranquility and accessibility. Enjoy easy access to local amenities, shopping centers, dining  options, and recreational facilities while savoring the privacy and serenity of country living.
